# Deep Malware Classification via Imaging

This repository contains the research project completed during the
NeuroScribe × Placewit 6-Week Research Internship Program.

The project focuses on converting malware binary files into grayscale
images and applying deep learning techniques for malware classification.
The repository includes the research report.

## Project Title
Transforming Binaries into Insights: Deep Malware Classification via Imaging

## Internship
NeuroScribe × Placewit  

## Work Overview
- Binary to image transformation  
- CNN-based malware classification  
- Model evaluation using standard metrics  

## Tools
Python, CNN, NumPy, Pandas, OpenCV, Scikit-learn 

